title: Late Nite Eats
overview: In each episode of Late Nite Eats, Jordan Andino visits a brand new city and three exceptional restaurants that reign supreme in the late night food scene! Each one is cooking up something truly spectacular and revolutionizing what it means to eat out long after dark. Jordan will meet these passionate chefs in their kitchens as they cook up their late night specialties, mingle with energetic diners and ultimately taste the most popular and delicious dishes that after hours eating has to offer.
